OL,3,CUrgent appeal for missing 11-year-old
OL,4,Cschoolboy
OL,6,FPolice have issued an urgent appeal
OL,7,Fafter an 11-year-old boy disappeared
OL,8,Ffrom his home.
OL,10,FGed Knox was last seen on Saturday 25
OL,11,FApril at around 11.30am after leaving
OL,12,Fhis home in Bromborough, Wirral.
OL,14,FHe is white, slim, 4ft 8in tall,with
OL,15,Fblonde hair and blue eyes, and wears
OL,16,Fglasses. Ged was last seen wearing a
OL,17,Fnavy blue Monitrex puffer coat, black
OL,18,Fshorts and black trainers.
OL,20,FHe has links to New Brighton and
OL,21,FBromborough.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/2
